<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-announces-first-robotic-pancreas-kidney-transplant-video/">Mayo Clinic announces first robotic pancreas-kidney transplant (VIDEO)</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
